{
  "texts": [
    "An example report reads: \"Skin, right melolabial fold, punch biopsy: Infiltrating basal cell carcinoma with variably clear cell features, lateral biopsy edge involved, see comment COMMENT: The carcinoma is confirmed by positivity to CK903.\"",
    "Radboud cohort.",
    "The COBRA 41 dataset contains 5147 slides from 4066 patients.",
    "All related slides were collected from the archives of the Department of Pathology at Radboud University Medical Center, scanned with a 3DHistech Pannoramic 1000 scanner (3DHistech, Hungary) at 20× magnification (pixel resolution 0.24 µm), and subsequently anonymized.",
    "The test set was used for evaluation."
  ]
}